        {
            "chapter": 80,
            "verse": 15,
            "text": "by the hands of angel-scribes"
        },
        {
            "chapter": 80,
            "verse": 16,
            "text": "honourable and virtuous"
        },
        {
            "chapter": 80,
            "verse": 17,
            "text": "Condemned are ˹disbelieving˺ humans! How ungrateful they are ˹to God˺"
        },
        {
            "chapter": 80,
            "verse": 18,
            "text": "From what substance did He create them"
